name: University of Washington
description: Web Services at the University of Washington is a method of getting important institutional data from and/or into your applications. Web Services are a way for applications or systems to talk to one another and does not usually involve human interaction. Currently, the use of Web Services is mainly targeted for application developers who would write code against them.
